            "title": "Flipster 推出 110 萬 USDT 質押計劃",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><img alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" src=\"https://image.theblockbeats.info/file_v6/20250309/d0ab4469-66ae-4f2b-8d91-981ec922c07e.jpg?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_50/format,webp\" style=\"\"/></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><img alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" src=\"https://image.theblockbeats.info/file_v6/20250309/d0ab4469-66ae-4f2b-8d91-981ec922c07e.jpg?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_50/format,webp\" style=\"\"/></p></section><section><p>2025 年 3 月 10 日－全球<a href=\"https://crypto.cnyes.com/BTC/24h\" target=\"_blank\">加密貨幣</a>交易所</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://m.theblockbeats.info/tw/news/57205\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color:#A9A9A9\">原文連結</a></p></section></main>",
